cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DC 

The paper discusses a conceptual model for intrusion detection in sensor networks using multi-agent systems and machine learning techniques. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and networked systems (cs.NI). The use of virtual robots and stigmergic variables also suggests a connection to systems and control (cs.SY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
